[[Field Transclusions]] of [[fields|Fields]], [[variables|Variables]], [[procedures|Procedures]], [[functions|Functions]], and [[macros|Macros]] are an essential part of TiddlyWiki. Here's the standard syntax for including bits and pieces from other places in a tiddler.

See [[Updated Summary of Transclusion Syntax]] for a more detailed treatment.

