    <td>{{Sn:WikitextTransclusionField||MagicSnippet}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Transclude an index from a [[data tiddler|Data Tiddlers]]</td>
    <td>(The [[Metadata]] tiddler contains details about //Grok TiddlyWiki// like its version number and project URL.)

    {{Sn:WikitextTransclusionData||MagicSnippet}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>[[Transclude a tiddler through a template|Templates and the Current Tiddler]]</td>
    <td>{{Sn:WikitextTransclusionTemplate||MagicSnippet}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Transclude the [[current tiddler|Templates and the Current Tiddler]] through a template</td>
